lxqt-nvmonitor (0.1-0ubuntu1) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Initial Ubuntu release.
    - NVIDIA GPU monitor plugin for LXQt panel.
    - Displays GPU utilization, VRAM load, VRAM usage, temperature,
      and power usage as a scrolling graph.

